<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
    <title>About Us - Ecommerce Outlaws</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/about.css">
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Barlow:wght@400;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
  </head>
  <body>
    <%- include('partials/navbar') %>

    <!-- ✅ HERO SECTION -->
    <section class="hero-about">
      <div class="container text-center">
        <h1>About US</h1>
        <p class="lead">Breaking fashion rules since day one. Built for rebels, worn by legends.</p>
        <div class="hero-stats">
          <div class="hero-stat">
            <h3>2020</h3>
            <p>Founded</p>
          </div>
          <div class="hero-stat">
            <h3>50K+</h3>
            <p>Happy Customers</p>
          </div>
          <div class="hero-stat">
            <h3>500+</h3>
            <p>Products</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ✅ WHO WE ARE -->
    <section class="about-section">
      <div class="container">
        <h2 class="section-title">Who We Are</h2>
        <p class="section-subtitle">We're not just another fashion brand. We're a movement of style rebels who refuse to follow the crowd.</p>
        
        <div class="row g-4">
          <div class="col-md-6">
            <div class="content-card">
              <div class="icon-box">
                <i class="fas fa-fire"></i>
              </div>
              <h3>Style Rebels</h3>
              <p>We believe fashion should be fearless. Every piece in our collection is designed for those who dare to stand out, make statements, and break conventional style rules.</p>
              <p>From streetwear essentials to bold statement pieces, we create clothing that empowers you to express your true self without compromise.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="col-md-6">
            <div class="content-card">
              <div class="icon-box">
                <i class="fas fa-users"></i>
              </div>
              <h3>Community Driven</h3>
              <p>Our community of outlaws spans across the globe. We're connected by a shared belief that fashion is personal, powerful, and should never be dictated by trends alone.</p>
              <p>Every design decision we make is influenced by feedback from our community of style rebels who aren't afraid to push boundaries.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ✅ OUR JOURNEY -->
    <section class="about-section alt">
      <div class="container">
        <h2 class="section-title">Our Journey</h2>
        <p class="section-subtitle">From a bold idea to a global fashion movement</p>
        
        <div class="timeline">
          <div class="timeline-item">
            <div class="timeline-date">2020</div>
            <div class="timeline-content">
              <h4>The Beginning</h4>
              <p>Started with a simple mission: create fashion for people who refuse to blend in. Our first collection launched with just 10 pieces but unlimited attitude.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="timeline-item">
            <div class="timeline-date">2021</div>
            <div class="timeline-content">
              <h4>Breaking Ground</h4>
              <p>Expanded our reach globally and introduced our signature "Outlaw" line. Our community grew to over 10,000 style rebels worldwide.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="timeline-item">
            <div class="timeline-date">2023</div>
            <div class="timeline-content">
              <h4>Going Digital</h4>
              <p>Launched our full e-commerce platform, making our rebellious fashion accessible to outlaws everywhere. Reached 50,000+ satisfied customers.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="timeline-item">
            <div class="timeline-date">2025</div>
            <div class="timeline-content">
              <h4>The Future</h4>
              <p>Continuing to push boundaries with sustainable fashion, limited drops, and exclusive collaborations. The revolution continues.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ✅ OUR VALUES -->
    <section class="about-section">
      <div class="container">
        <h2 class="section-title">Our Values</h2>
        <p class="section-subtitle">The principles that drive everything we do</p>
        
        <div class="values-grid">
          <div class="value-card">
            <div class="icon">
              <i class="fas fa-fist-raised"></i>
            </div>
            <h4>Authenticity</h4>
            <p>We believe in staying true to yourself. Our designs celebrate individuality and encourage you to express your unique style without compromise.</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="value-card">
            <div class="icon">
              <i class="fas fa-leaf"></i>
            </div>
            <h4>Sustainability</h4>
            <p>Fashion shouldn't cost the earth. We're committed to sustainable practices, ethical manufacturing, and creating pieces that last.</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="value-card">
            <div class="icon">
              <i class="fas fa-award"></i>
            </div>
            <h4>Quality</h4>
            <p>Every piece is crafted with attention to detail and built to last. We believe in creating investment pieces, not disposable fashion.</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="value-card">
            <div class="icon">
              <i class="fas fa-rocket"></i>
            </div>
            <h4>Innovation</h4>
            <p>We're always pushing boundaries, exploring new materials, designs, and ways to disrupt the traditional fashion industry.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ✅ OUR GOALS -->
    <section class="about-section alt">
      <div class="container">
        <h2 class="section-title">Our Goals</h2>
        <p class="section-subtitle">Where we're heading and what drives us forward</p>
        
        <div class="row g-4">
          <div class="col-lg-4">
            <div class="content-card text-center">
              <div class="icon-box">
                <i class="fas fa-globe"></i>
              </div>
              <h3>Global Impact</h3>
              <p>Expand our community of style rebels to every corner of the world, making fearless fashion accessible to all who dare to be different.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="col-lg-4">
            <div class="content-card text-center">
              <div class="icon-box">
                <i class="fas fa-recycle"></i>
              </div>
              <h3>Sustainable Future</h3>
              <p>Lead the fashion industry toward a more sustainable future with innovative materials and ethical production practices.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="col-lg-4">
            <div class="content-card text-center">
              <div class="icon-box">
                <i class="fas fa-heart"></i>
              </div>
              <h3>Community First</h3>
              <p>Build the strongest community of fashion rebels who support each other and celebrate individual expression.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <%- include('partials/footer') %>
    
    <!-- Bootstrap JS -->
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
    
    <!-- About Page Interactions -->
    <script src="/js/about.js"></script>
  </body>
</html>
